Marjorie Daw (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marjorie_Daw_(actress) 0 Marjorie Daw (born Margaret House, January 19, 1902 – March 18, 1979) was an American film actress of the silent film era. She appeared in 76 films between 1914 and 1929. Marjorie_Daw ( born Margaret_House , January_19_,_1902 – March_18_,_1979 ) was an_American_film_actress of the_silent_film_era .
